{"tid":215742,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[不服來辯]同性戀根本就係錯事","createTime":"2017-04-24T15:18:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T23:48:15.000Z","uid":29880,"like":15,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e7cf425d02e637110a4ea2b2abd7e88a641554dd","tid":215742,"uid":29880,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T15:18:42.000Z","msg":"同性戀根本違反生理<br />\n如果一種生物本性係會鍾意同性<br />\n咁就繁衍唔到後代,好快絕種<br />\n<br />\n雖然同性戀係少數<br />\n呢一刻地球咁多人<br />\n你可能覺得D人同性戀生少D係好事<br />\n但風氣一長就一發不可收拾<br />\n你可能會覺得冇可能<br />\n但喺呢個仍然未完全接受同性戀嘅世界<br />\n同性戀嘅人己經越黎越多<br />\n如果完全接受,變相等於鼓勵<br />\n越黎越多人同性戀<br />\n同性戀情侶冇後代<br />\n又影響埋領養嘅細路<br />\n之後就骨牌效應<br />\n人口銳減,經濟崩潰<br />\n到時就恨錯難返<br />\n<br />\n所以鼓勵同性戀(e.g.同性婚姻合法化)<br />\n根本係慢性絕種<br />\n我都好同情同性戀者<br />\n但好抱歉呢個世界總會有弱勢嘅小眾"},{"pid":"2e5c8c6faceb659d64536a3f8ef9acd65f26c99f","tid":215742,"uid":35906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T15:22:58.000Z","msg":"人哋鍾意 關你撚事咩 又唔係雞姦你 又唔係鍾意你"},{"pid":"b49b33321f59adc88fa5392cb34d312e4fb1ffd9","tid":215742,"uid":69528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T15:25:01.000Z","msg":"人類慢性絕種對地球利多於弊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c1906442eca8be4f945dd37dbf13c902447cc70","tid":215742,"uid":24623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T15:26:12.000Z","msg":"假設同性戀變得「流行」 你會唔會變gay?"},{"pid":"0322d7c15a805affa440e2a41536633589b3d261","tid":215742,"uid":36603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T15:31:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人類慢性絕種對地球利多於弊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e51d2ac705c2ce50168babaa4612faabfde313","tid":215742,"uid":105908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T15:39:52.000Z","msg":"呢條友鳩吹左個theory，無乜support，但算係另一個角度可以睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=17EqZEf6wBk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D17EqZEf6wBk&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8Y9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=22483c09\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=17EqZEf6wBk</a>"},{"pid":"5549a7f5798646c2927b802f5770a4a21a7a1137","tid":215742,"uid":97451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T15:47:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"025b3069a9579f3ae722d609dd4b9443b7596b5f","tid":215742,"uid":93266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T15:51:49.000Z","msg":"人口銳減咪減囉..<br />\n<br />\n經濟崩潰咪崩潰囉..<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到時我人都死左 , 真係關我戀事...   <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0917cd49e66bd5d4c2f897afe19a84d3863c63","tid":215742,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T15:53:45.000Z","msg":"同性戀造成世界末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同性婚姻唔係叫你搞基，<br />\n異性戀唔會因為立左條法就轉基。<br />\n另外，今日有人工受孕，<br />\n科技可以解決到，咁就無問題啦。"},{"pid":"f67a800f97d4f8405510885c6c8c0e1408534f05","tid":215742,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T15:57:30.000Z","msg":"樓主有冇睇過關於   老鼠烏托邦  既實驗<br />\n現代社會出現同性戀其實都唔奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4-NhkNgdStQ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4-NhkNgdStQ%20&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8Y9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=abc9625f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4-NhkNgdStQ </a>"},{"pid":"032c424d20a0d4ea03dd68dbb56c1e74558d5407","tid":215742,"uid":50290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T16:00:39.000Z","msg":"好撚過你, 你自己一個最後咪又係戇鳩鳩訓棺材, 你自己同你老母交配啦"},{"pid":"227eb326d5199764bdfb0cfa357bfd2e7c29fb2e","tid":215742,"uid":100082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T16:02:22.000Z","msg":"最on9既係同性戀唔會因為多左人接受而變多，只會因為冇咁多人歧視而變得敢面對自己既取向<br />\n<br />\n同性戀唔係病毒，唔會因爲多左人接受而變多"},{"pid":"42ea6c753df0157ac324d410f7441cf1da9c518e","tid":215742,"uid":93142,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T16:27:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同性戀根本違反生理<br />\n如果一種生物本性係會鍾意同性<br />\n咁就繁衍唔到後代,好快絕種</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1. 生理＝？ 唔只人類，好多高等動物（猩猩，雀仔等等）都有同性戀現象，而暫時未搵到任何基因／遺傳上既連繫。<br />\n<br />\n2. 你用人類既人口地理學（population geography）去同其他生物既繁殖方式比已經有好多問題。1. 生物會鐘意同性不等如每一個個體都鐘意同性 2. 人類都可以用體外繁殖。如果繁衍到後代，唔會絕種，就冇問題？<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n同性戀嘅人己經越黎越多<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇多到，亦冇少到，只係而家社會風氣開始接受，所以多左人講。古羅馬同古希臘都有同性戀，仲要幾common。同樣道理，咁唔代表其他國家／時代冇，只係古羅馬同古希臘比較接受。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n如果完全接受,變相等於鼓勵<br />\n越黎越多人同性戀<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  接受＝鼓勵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n同性戀情侶冇後代<br />\n又影響埋領養嘅細路<br />\n之後就骨牌效應<br />\n人口銳減,經濟崩潰<br />\n到時就恨錯難返<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Slippery slope 自己查<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n所以鼓勵同性戀(e.g.同性婚姻合法化)<br />\n根本係慢性絕種<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁係咪唔會絕種就冇問題？你認為人生既目的就係生仔？<br />\n<br />\n本來就膠都廢事派，不過見你放喺學術台就陪你吹下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647609681629aa059d3c212e58546109f2bc3fdc","tid":215742,"uid":31739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T16:34:01.000Z","msg":"人類幾時開始以自然嘅法則黎當做道德?"},{"pid":"d9d8a7e2ee7346939a16975ecd8da0e77b854181","tid":215742,"uid":15730,"lik