都廢事派，不過見你放喺學術台就陪你吹下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n秒左樓豬👍🏿"},{"pid":"3cfc70f32d7f50692884dfb6d7d8050d8460e80e","tid":215742,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T17:10:00.000Z","msg":"#1<del>世界</del>真摟屌"},{"pid":"91e5a6f05ddf99a47455a07a7a5ef8fb03a7b5a4","tid":215742,"uid":104447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T17:33:59.000Z","msg":"個社會接受傷殘人士 =&gt; 鼓勵啲人變成傷殘?"},{"pid":"711e18de82ff2d01bafd70c2820365fe5f1f8fee","tid":215742,"uid":110699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T23:48:15.000Z","msg":"同性戀雖然好嘔心，不過人哋冇搞鳩你<br />\n你就唔好搞人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}